title: RTB Social Media #4: Marketing Campaigns / Tracking Codes by Page Views, Sessions, by Month

dashboard_elements.note_text:
Purpose: View page views and sessions results for marketing campaigns associated with RTB pages.
Social media-related campaigns with specific labeling can be filtered for here. For example, using the initials "FB" for Facebook campaigns.
Page views are broken down by month. Use the Date filter to change the date as needed.

More Information: To learn more about web analytics definitions for metrics and how to navigate standard dashboards, go to the Web Analytics Guide.
